# Patch:        paddle.fluid → paddle.base / paddle.nn.functional (Paddle 2.6 / Python 3.11 兼容)
# Reason:       Paddle 2.6 (本项目锁定的 paddlepaddle-gpu==2.6.2 wheel) 已**移除** paddle.fluid 子包.
#               上游 PaddleVideo release/2.2.0 在多个 backbone / head / utils 文件中 import 旧位置, 触发
#               `ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'paddle.fluid'` 与
#               `AttributeError: module 'paddle' has no attribute 'fluid'`.
#
#               迁移映射:
#                 paddle.fluid.framework.Variable    → paddle.base.framework.Variable
#                 paddle.fluid.framework.in_dygraph_mode → paddle.base.framework.in_dygraph_mode
#                 paddle.fluid.core                  → paddle.base.core
#                 paddle.fluid.layer_helper.LayerHelper → paddle.base.layer_helper.LayerHelper
#                 paddle.fluid.dygraph (layers)      → 本上游未实际使用此 import; 删除
#                 paddle.fluid.dygraph.to_variable   → paddle.base.dygraph.to_variable
#                 paddle.fluid.data_feeder.*         → paddle.base.data_feeder.*
#                 paddle.fluid.layers.pad            → paddle.nn.functional.pad (注意 paddings 参数顺序)
#                 paddle.fluid.layers.temporal_shift → paddle.nn.functional.temporal_shift
#                 paddle.fluid.core.is_compiled_with_npu() → False  (paddle 2.6 移除了 NPU 探测; 本项目不上 NPU)
#                 paddle.fluid.core.VarBase          → paddle.Tensor  (eager-mode 统一; VarBase 已移除)
#
# 验证:
#   `paddlevideo.modeling.builder.build_model` 能成功构建 PP-TSM (Recognizer2D, 24.4M 参数);
#   随机张量 [1, 8, 3, 224, 224] 经 forward 得到形状 [1, 400] 的有限输出.
#
# Upstream PR:  none (release/2.2.0 已是 frozen 分支)
# Tested on:    da9a8ce8f0beba020727c7e7b6c50308d32df76f  (release/2.2.0 tip) + paddlepaddle-gpu==2.6.2
# Removable when: 升级到含修复的更高 PaddleVideo release; 或 fork 上游做合并.
